It could also belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL) as it involves natural language processing and speech recognition. 

The paper may also fall under the arXiv CS sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it uses neural networks and backpropagation for optimization. 

Furthermore, it could be categorized under the arXiv CS sub-category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) as it involves neural network-based approaches for speech processing.
